    • Uses of FilterServlet in de.db.derpate.servlet

      Subclasses of FilterServlet in de.db.derpate.servlet 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  ChangePasswordServlet
      This HttpServlet can be used by Godfathers and Admins to change their own password.
      Allowed methods: POST
      class  GodfatherFilterServlet
      This servlet is only available for Trainees and is used to filter available godfathers or - if the trainee already selected a godfahter - get information of their selected godfather.
      class  GodfatherImageServlet
      This HttpServlet is available for Trainees only and is used to get the image of a Godfather (set by Godfather).
      If no image is found (because the Godfather hasn't set one), error 404 is returned.
      class  LoginServlet
      This HttpServlet get's called by the client, when the user tries to log on.
      class  LogoutServlet
      This HttpServlet is used to remove the relation between the client's HttpSession and the logged in LoginUser.
      Allowed http methods: GET

      Subclasses of FilterServlet in de.db.derpate.servlet.adminOnly 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  GenerateTraineeTokenServlet
      This HttpServlet may be used by a Admin to generate new Tokens, that can be used by Trainees to login
      Allowed http methods: GET
      class  GodfatherAddServlet
      This HttpServlet can be used by Admins to add a Godfather account.
      class  GodfatherUpdateServlet
      This Servlet is used by the Admin to update a Godfathers personal data (except password) or to remove the Godfather
      Allowed http methods: POST, DELETE
      class  TraineeRemoveServlet
      This servlet can be used to remove a Trainees Godfather (POST) or to delete the Trainees account itself (DELETE).
      Allowed http methods: POST, DELETE
